00:12:30.924 --> 00:12:34.324
This type I interferon results in T cell recruitment.

214
00:12:34.524 --> 00:12:37.763
These T cells become activated, and they're required for PARP inhibitor

215
00:12:37.864 --> 00:12:39.044
monotherapy

216
00:12:40.304 --> 00:12:43.273
efficacy. We also saw increase in PD-L1.

217
00:12:44.364 --> 00:12:48.214
And so, this really suggested that potentially we could

218
00:12:48.244 --> 00:12:52.144
enhance PARP inhibitor responses by adding a T cell

