228
00:13:24.224 --> 00:13:27.924
And so we asked, "How could this be possible that if you're

229
00:13:27.964 --> 00:13:31.764
getting interferon responses to the

230
00:13:31.804 --> 00:13:33.964
PARP inhibitor, you're getting more T cells.

231
00:13:34.304 --> 00:13:37.724
Why isn't the immune checkpoint blockade working to enhance PARP inhibitor

232
00:13:37.764 --> 00:13:39.784
responses?" Well, you know

233
00:13:40.964 --> 00:13:44.944
the punchline. We hypothesized it was the lipid-associated

