00:34:04.884 --> 00:34:08.245
And we've taken this long view approach where we have to create both a platform for

602
00:34:08.265 --> 00:34:11.884
discovery and translation, and that's built on two pillars.

603
00:34:12.004 --> 00:34:15.884
One is we have to understand the problem better to create the foundational data

