00:34:15.964 --> 00:34:17.884
sets to understand these myeloid cells,

605
00:34:18.745 --> 00:34:20.614
and we use single cell RNA sequencing,

606
00:34:21.444 --> 00:34:25.284
spatial transcriptomics, and increasingly spatial proteomic data sets to

607
00:34:25.304 --> 00:34:26.084
