608
00:34:27.064 --> 00:34:30.504
And the second really important arm is we have to have a functional model system

609
00:34:30.544 --> 00:34:34.185
where we can test human myeloid cells in matched human cancer

610
00:34:34.205 --> 00:34:38.063
cells. And I was really lucky during my postdoc that Penn came out

