00:41:02.072 --> 00:41:04.212
immune cells into that microenvironment.

731
00:41:05.322 --> 00:41:08.412
And then the microgli inflammatory program, which is really brain specific, it's

732
00:41:08.452 --> 00:41:10.411
the default inflammatory program for microgli.

733
00:41:10.432 --> 00:41:12.532
They see an inflammatory stimulus, they express this program.

734
00:41:13.292 --> 00:41:16.032
Then you have two immunosuppressive programs.

735
00:41:16.052 --> 00:41:19.082
They were expressed in different cells within the tumor in different places

