00:57:46.020 --> 00:57:49.900
We don't put anything else in there except putting monocytes

1029
00:57:50.080 --> 00:57:53.369
with the organoid, and there's enough signal there from the tumor cells and

1030
00:57:53.400 --> 00:57:57.240
whatever else is in that organoid that it signals for that cell to go under

1031
00:57:57.500 --> 00:57:58.080
pyroptosis.

1032
00:57:58.780 --> 00:57:59.660
Okay. Yep. Thanks.

1033
00:58:01.720 --> 00:58:05.660
Hi. Thank you for your talk again. I'm curious how your

