00:58:38.520 --> 00:58:42.380
Yeah. Great question. It's something we're actively studying, and we have a sort

1046
00:58:42.420 --> 00:58:45.119
of breast cancer brain met program going on in the lab.

1047
00:58:47.040 --> 00:58:50.320
At least in GBM, so lower grade gliomas, more

1048
00:58:50.360 --> 00:58:52.740
microglia than bone marrow-derived macrophages.

1049
00:58:52.800 --> 00:58:56.640
But in GBM, there's a lot of bone marrow-derived macrophages, and probably, we

