00:59:22.920 --> 00:59:25.000
myeloid programs in the brain mets as well.

1059
00:59:25.300 --> 00:59:28.690
Okay. Like with the IL-1 beta, that-

1060
00:59:28.800 --> 00:59:28.980
Yeah.

1061
00:59:30.300 --> 00:59:33.300
I don't know specifically for that story, if it's exactly the same thing that we're

