00:59:39.280 --> 00:59:41.079
brain mets. Slightly different, but similar.

1065
00:59:41.500 --> 00:59:42.040
Thank you.

1066
00:59:42.100 --> 00:59:42.180
Yeah.

1067
00:59:43.520 --> 00:59:43.680
Great.

